info.author: David Jonas
info.description:
Introduction
============

An installable theme for Plone 4

Changelog
=========
0.97 (2016-04-12)
---------------------
- Adaptation to the changes on the addthis sharing templates CSS. [andreg]

0.96 (2014-03-19)
---------------------
- Adaptation to the changes on the twitter addthis sharing templates. 

0.95 (2013-12-12)
---------------------
- Cropping scale now spans through all the views.
- Adaptation for the upgrade to fourdigits.portlet.twitter

0.94 (2013-08-19)
---------------------
- Donation forms changed and ordering the related items on document view.

0.93 (2013-07-08)
---------------------
- Fix in the merged views that blocked the cropping interface.

0.92 (2013-07-05)
---------------------
- Merging back because of event work that was unfinished on the repository

0.91 (2013-07-05)
---------------------
- Added videos to the blog view.

0.90 (2013-05-22)
---------------------
- Small fixes for Plone 4.3

0.89 (2013-04-24)
---------------------
- Added support for flags with tags with spaces.

0.88 (2013-04-24)
---------------------
- fix on image view.

0.87 (2013-04-24)
---------------------
- New colors for tags

0.86 (2013-04-24)
---------------------
- Image cropping support.
- Scales on generic setup.
- Do not allow access to full screen picture view.  

0.85 (2013-03-13)
---------------------
- Added javascript to track the forms added on the body of pages with GA.

0.84 (2013-03-13)
---------------------
- Changed "After today" criteria on collections to match the expected behaviour of events view.
- Events just become past in the end of the day.
- Fixed the event listing view to conform with the above change.

0.83 (2013-03-12)
---------------------
- CSS fixes, more cross browser testing and aded up link on Link types.

0.82 (2013-03-12)
---------------------
- More cross browser resposive design tweaking for iPhone and Android devices.
- Presskit link on document_view was not testing for the right permissions.

0.81 (2013-03-06)
---------------------
- Fixed the layout for better accessibility when using the large fonts

0.80 (2013-03-06)
---------------------
- Adjusted the actions.xml file.

0.79 (2013-03-06)
---------------------
- Activated mobile zooming without breaking the layout.
- Added new permission to control who can mark buyable content.
- Automatically add forms on buyable content.

0.78 (2013-03-05)
---------------------
- Fluid layout fixes for cross-browser compatibility
- Reset hour format to default

0.77 (2013-02-28)
---------------------
- Accessibility issues.

0.76 (2013-02-27)
---------------------
- Bugfixing round on CSS/JS for mobiles

0.75 (2013-02-27)
---------------------
- Fix on today events.
- Changed fonts.

0.74 (2013-02-21)
---------------------
- Changed the date formats.

0.73 (2013-02-21)
---------------------
- Removed the stray images from the people listing

0.72 (2013-02-21)
---------------------
- Changes to the people view

0.71 (2013-02-19)
---------------------
- Adaptation to the new version of collective.media

0.70 (2013-02-18)
---------------------
- Mobile tweaks

0.69 (2013-02-18)
---------------------
- Revised colors

0.68 (2013-02-18)
---------------------
- Adding the donation button to free events.

0.67 (2013-02-18)
---------------------
- Added more colors to the tag flags;
- Fix on the front page slideshow;

0.66 (2013-02-15)
---------------------
- JS and CSS fixes for responsive layout.

0.65 (2013-02-14)
---------------------
- Adapted collective carousel to the front page view to show featured items.

0.64 (2013-02-13)
---------------------
- Disabling dependency on unreleased version of Products.mediaPerson

0.63 (2013-02-13)
---------------------
- Multiple bugfixes and CSS tweaks on alignments
- Slideshow improvement
- Files and images get a level up link
- Tag flags stay on

0.62 (2013-02-12)
---------------------
- Bug fixing in CSS alignments and slideshow.
- Colored Flags.

0.61 (2013-01-31)
---------------------
- Override collective.mediaShow to add parent descriptions when the images does not have one.

0.60 (2013-01-31)
---------------------
- Fixed manual portlet override with the new URLs

0.59 (2013-01-30)
---------------------
- Removing left over debug code from JS

0.58 (2013-01-30)
---------------------
- Fix on Blog view

0.57 (2013-01-30)
---------------------
- Javascript tweaks, Booking information.

0.56 (2013-01-30)
---------------------
- Fix on event_listing custom view. Typo.

0.55 (2013-01-30)
---------------------
- Make presskits download directly if you cant edit them. 

0.54 (2013-01-24)
---------------------
- More presskit customizations
- Fixed a crash when tiling collections without description.

0.53 (2013-01-23)
---------------------
- Form CSS.
- Design for mailchimp portlet.

0.52 (2013-01-23)
---------------------
- Share counter with popup.

0.51 (2013-01-23)
---------------------
- New design for share buttons.

0.50 (2013-01-23)
---------------------
- PressKit design and adaptations.
- AddThis share buttons.

0.49 (2013-01-22)
---------------------
- Quick fix on CSS of portlet headers.

0.48 (2013-01-22)
---------------------
- Change on the override of Manual related portlet.
- Small bugfix of an extra comma on event dates.

0.47 (2013-01-16)
---------------------
- Overriding the twitter template to add a link to follow.
- Multiple CSS/structure fixes.
- Override for the manual related portlet.

0.46 (2013-01-15)
---------------------
- Added media back to the search results.

0.45 (2013-01-15)
---------------------
- fix on the collective media usage

0.44 (2013-01-15)
---------------------
- adjusted line heights.
- added CSS for collective.twitter.portlets

0.43 (2013-01-14)
---------------------
- Fluid layout cross-browser testing.
- Bugfixes
- First attempt to add leading media to collections

0.42 (2013-01-14)
---------------------
- Added a three column view option for all folders and collections

0.41 (2013-01-11)
---------------------
- quick CSS fix on column layout

0.40 (2013-01-11)
---------------------
- Added a new three column design. Better adaptability
- Bugfixing round.

0.39 (2013-01-11)
---------------------
- Cross-browser testing and design cleanup.

0.38 (2013-01-10)
---------------------
- Override of site actions portlet and added sponsors instead;

0.37 (2013-01-10)
---------------------
- Updated to the new slideshow layout with dynamic height calculation.

0.36 (2013-01-09)
---------------------
- fixed CSS size of the text in the listings.

0.35 (2013-01-09)
---------------------
- Added the custom weekday messages for today's events

0.34 (2013-01-08)
---------------------
- Bugfixing round. visual and backend.

0.33 (2013-01-03)
---------------------
- Very small CSS fix on the calendar portlet.

0.32 (2013-01-03)
---------------------
- Changed cropping of the images.
- Removed document by line from the front page.
- Portlet that renders content depending on the day of the week.

0.31 (2013-01-03)
---------------------
- More CSS and JS on the front-page view. Responsive design on the portlets of the front page portlet managers.

0.30 (2013-01-02)
---------------------
- Added a front page view with two portlet managers and the main content that comes from a collection namef "/arnolfini/front_page_main" 

0.29 (2012-12-19)
---------------------
- CSS fixing on alignemt of page wrappers.

0.28 (2012-12-19)
---------------------
- Added metadata configuration for hasMedia to be visible on collections
- Collection portlet override and related items portlet override.

0.27 (2012-12-18)
---------------------
- Lots of javascript features such as masonry on portlets for small screen sizes.
- Number of results appears automatically in portlet list of links of collections.

0.26 (2012-12-17)
---------------------
- Bugfixing round.

0.25 (2012-12-13)
---------------------
- Configuring portlet areas to all templates and screen sizes;
- Configuring the calendar portlet

0.24 (2012-12-12)
---------------------
- Slideshow CSS fix.

0.23 (2012-12-12)
---------------------
- Added and CSS Menu
- Blog view

0.22 (2012-12-12)
---------------------
- Merged archive view with event view.

0.21 (2012-12-12)
---------------------
- Added event listing view and folder listing view.

0.20 (2012-12-10)
---------------------
- removing getpaid dependency on ZCML

0.19 (2012-12-10)
---------------------
- Work on the new document_view that also renders events now.
- Archive portlet shows now only if event is past.
- Added functions to test if event is past and to format dates.

0.18 (2012-12-10)
---------------------
- Bugfix on search results throwing an error when "bodyless" items are a result. 

0.17 (2012-12-06)
---------------------
- Added archive button to the portlet

0.16 (2012-12-06)
---------------------
- 404 page.

0.15 (2012-12-05)
---------------------
- changes on the slideshow behaviour.
- event to create a slideshow folder automatically on each item of Media types.

0.14 (2012-12-04)
---------------------
- Search view and people view;

0.13 (2012-12-04)
---------------------
- CSS tweaks and bugfixing

0.12 (2012-11-29)
---------------------
- Default to show only documented events
- button to show all events
- popup leads to all events

0.11 (2012-11-29)
---------------------
- folder listing view
- fixes on the portlets and ordering
- CSS

0.10 (2012-11-28)
---------------------
- Added anothe archive portlet.
- CSS fixes
- Added popup before opening undocumented years.

0.9 (2012-11-27)
---------------------
- Optimized archival views using collective.media.

0.8 (2012-11-20)
---------------------
- Added show all years functionality to archive.

0.7 (2012-11-20)
---------------------
- Removed dependency on viewportletmanager.

0.6 (2012-11-20)
---------------------
- Adding the first archive design prototype.

0.5 (2012-11-16)
---------------------
- Starting the views

0.4 (2012-11-13)
---------------------
- Footer CSS alignments revised

0.3 (2012-11-13)
---------------------
- Fixes for safari.

0.2 (unreleased)
----------------

- Footer work, portlet manager on the footer

0.1dev (unreleased)
-------------------

- Initial release
